The '''Comité d'études sur les formations d'ingénieurs''' ('''CEFI''', in English '''engineer training studies committee''')<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.challenges.fr/magazine/20110224.CHA5178/quelle-penurie-d-ingenieurs.html Quelle pénurie d'ingénieurs?]</ref> is the [[France|French]] institution which studies the questions of training and job placement for [[engineers]] in [[France]], in partnership with associations like the CNISF (National Council of Engineers and Scientists of France). Created in 1975 by French [[Ministry of National Education (France)|Ministry of National Education]], after that it became an association representing engineers associations, ''[[grandes écoles]]''<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.cge.asso.fr/en/nos-membres/organismes/32-comite-d-etudes-sur-les-formations-d-ingenieur Comité d'études sur les formations d'ingénieur]{{dead link|date=August 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> and companies.<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.cnisf.org/page_dyn.php?page_id=MDAwMDAwMDEzNw== Comité Etudes sur Formation Ingénieurs]{{dead link|date=August 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> 

The CEFI has a website with information concerning educational system in France and job placement for graduates.<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.cdefi.fr/10107345/0/fiche___pagelibre/&RH=CDE_ACCUEIL&RF=1141910077485 Partenaires] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120705004728/http://www.cdefi.fr/10107345/0/fiche___pagelibre/%26RH%3DCDE_ACCUEIL%26RF%3D1141910077485 |date=2012-07-05 }}</ref><ref>{{fr icon}} [http://wheb.ac-reims.fr/cio/Reims/index.php?option=com_weblinks&view=category&id=52%3Asites-dinformation-sur-les-etudes-formations&Itemid=69 CEFI]</ref> 

Sometimes, it performs studies for schools<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.phosphore.com/contenu_connexe_ges/266/formation/140031 International : les écoles d'ingénieurs à l'heure de la mondialisation] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120511063933/http://www.phosphore.com/contenu_connexe_ges/266/formation/140031 |date=2012-05-11 }}</ref> or partners companies.<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://rechercheformation.revues.org/844 Les formations d’ingénieurs. Des formations professionnelles et professionnalisantes. Orientations, contenus, contextes]</ref>

